snippet.title: Summon Night: Swordcraft Story 2 Intro (1080p 60FPS)
snippet.description: Summon Night: Swordcraft Story 2 is an action role-playing game by Banpresto for the Nintendo Game Boy Advance system. It is part of the Summon Night series of games and the sequel to Summon Night: Swordcraft Story. Atlus handled the English translation of the game.
